						 <p>I wasn't an especially big fan of this. As a concept, I'm totally down with it. Building somehow being tortured? Sweet! However, the execution left a lot to be desired. The interview quickly became irritating rather than entertaining, and the humorous premise didn't outweigh the lack of a satisfying conclusion.</p> 
